invariant socket_extra77.SocketKind_mro5_name_object:
  description: "socket.SocketKind.__mro__[5].__name__.__eq__('object') == True — last element of SocketKind 6-element MRO is object; extra15 covers mro[1]=='IntEnum'; extra35 covers mro len; no prior socket spec checks SocketKind.__mro__[5].__name__; first MRO[5] name standalone for SocketKind"
  category: class_attrs
